title: "Sunnyside AI: Multi-Agent PV Solar Simulation Platform"
abstract: "A multi-agent AI system for photovoltaic (PV) solar system design and energy production simulation, combining open LLMs with physics-based PVlib calculations. Features battery storage optimization, PLN tariff calculator, and professional PDF report generation."
